            . I am a Police-constable. I was in Portland-place when the pot-boy told me of the prisoners; I followed them, and knocked off their hats - I found this quart pot in Pearce's hat, and the other pint pot belonging to Radway in his acket pocket - Sellers had the other pint.</p>
